okensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"TagComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tags"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") and borders","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","title":"OrangeT